      "title": "Fuel for health workers today (15)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ministry of Health says that dedicated day for distributing fuel for health staff will be in effect today (15).",
        "The Ministry further said that fuel will be issued at 109 selected filling stations for health staff.",
        "Accordingly, the Ministry of Health says that 20L of fuel will be issued for a car, 8L of fuel for three-wheelers, and 6L of fuel for a motorcycle.",
        "Parliament to meet on 20th July to elect new President; Nominations on 19th July"
      ],
